    "description": "<strong>Maid's Melancholy</strong> is a puzzle game where you become a maid and perform various tasks. 'Clara', an apprentice maid, has to perform various tasks at the Belmond House in order to become a full-time maid recognized by the state. Can Clara safely pass the exam and become a full-time maid?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Various minigames</strong><br>You can play about 10 mini-games such as serving, hunting, cleaning, and more! Aim for the highest score in each minigame!<br><br></li><li><strong>Various Achievements</strong><br>There are more than 30 different achievement elements in Maid's Melancholy. Achieve numerous achievements in the game!</li></ul>",
